Neverthink is what happens when channel surfing and YouTube collide.
This video app doesn't let you rewind, skip or pause. There is just a grid of channels with different genres to choose from – Funny, AWWW, Learn Something, News, Music, Basketball and plenty more.
Tap a channel, and you'll be thrown directly into a video (and just as with traditional TV, it might be halfway through when you join). Perhaps you'll see three minutes of recipes and cooking ideas on the Lifestyle channel. On the Beauty channel, you could end up watching a popular YouTube star talking about makeup.
